    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i just had the weirdest thing happen. i was just sitting in the library and suddenly got this insane headache, like a massive bolt of lightning just hit my head. it was super intense for a second but it's kind of fading now, just leaving me feeling a bit weird and foggy. i think i've just been drinking way too much coffee and not enough water today. do u think i just need to hydrate and sleep it off or something? it felt so sudden though.",
