    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah that's what i thought too. it's just kinda annoying and making it hard to focus on my studying. i'm feeling a bit lightheaded but probably just need some electrolytes or something. do you think i should take some ibuprofen or something to make sure it doesn't come back? i really don't want to go to the clinic if i don't have to, it's such a hassle.",
