    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks, that makes sense. i'll just grab a gatorade and some advil. i'm also kinda worried about this feeling in my neck though, it feels super stiff and tight, like i pulled something, but i didn't even move weirdly. it's probably just stress from finals, right? i don't really want to spend the whole night in an ER waiting room if it's just a bad tension headache. you're pretty sure i'm fine to just sleep it off?",
